# Galbrena — Combat Kit & Mechanics

## Galbrena: Combat Archetype and Role
- **Element / Attribute:** Fusion
- **Weapon Type:** Pistols
- **Role:** Main DPS (on-field carry; burst damage specialist)
- **Scaling Stat:** ATK (ATK-scaling kit)
- **Damage Types:** Heavy Attack DMG (majority), Echo Skill DMG (key finisher stages)
- **Combat Style:** Stance-switcher; builds Sinflame resource in default Threshold State, then enters Demon Hypostasis (enhanced stance) by consuming Sinflame for amplified close-range burst damage using pistols and wing-blades
- **Specialty:** Single-target boss damage; T0 rating in Tower of Adversity; strongest Fusion Main DPS as of Patch 2.7–3.0

## Galbrena: Key Resources (Forte Mechanics Overview)
- **Sinflame (Blue Bar):** Holds up to 100 points. Recovered in Threshold State by landing Basic Attacks, Heavy Attacks, Mid-air Attacks, Resonance Skill – Encroach, and Intro Skill. At 100 points, Resonance Skill transforms into Resonance Skill – Ascent of Malice, which triggers entry into Demon Hypostasis.
- **Purging Flame:** Converted 1:1 from Sinflame upon entering Demon Hypostasis (max 100 points). All Forte-enhanced attacks in Demon Hypostasis consume Purging Flame on hit. Demon Hypostasis ends when Purging Flame is depleted or after 50 seconds.
- **Afterflame (Red Bar):** Holds up to 40 points. Recovered in Threshold State by having any Resonator on the nearby team cast an Echo Skill (8 points per cast; same Echo name cannot trigger twice; resets on exiting Demon Hypostasis). All Afterflame is consumed upon entering Demon Hypostasis. Each point of Afterflame consumed grants +1.5% DMG Taken debuff on enemies during Demon Hypostasis (up to +60% at max 40 points). This is the rarest multiplier type in the game — effectively a multiplicative damage increase on all of Galbrena's in-stance attacks.
- **Fated End (Inherent Skill 1):** A stacking debuff applied to enemies, up to 4 stacks, each granting +5% DMG Amplification to Galbrena's direct damage for 5.5s.
- **Burning Drive (Forte Passive):** Casting Intro Skill, Hellstride, Basic Attack Stage 4, Resonance Skill – Encroach, Resonance Skill – Ascent of Malice, or Resonance Skill – Ravage grants Galbrena +20% ATK for 4 seconds.

