## Galbrena: Stats Baseline — Max Level Analysis
At Lv. 90, Galbrena has a moderately high ATK base (463) with standard HP/DEF values for a DPS Resonator. Her Max Energy of 125 is relatively high, requiring careful Energy Regen substat planning. Her base CRIT Rate (5%) and CRIT DMG (150%) are standard. Recommended endgame stat targets with full Echo build: ATK 1,900–2,100+, CRIT Rate 60–80% (pre-Echo set bonuses), CRIT DMG 230–270%+, Fusion DMG Bonus 40–70%+, Energy Regen 110–125%.

