## Galbrena: Resonance Skill: Edge Transcended
Two forms depending on current Sinflame.

**Resonance Skill – Encroach (default):**
Dash forward, leap into air, flip backward on hit — deals Fusion DMG (Heavy Attack DMG).
- Cooldown: 5s

**Resonance Skill – Ascent of Malice (at 100 Sinflame):**
Slash at enemies with wings dealing Fusion DMG (Heavy Attack DMG). Triggers Demon Hypostasis entry. Converts all Sinflame to Purging Flame. Consumes all Afterflame to grant Fusion DMG Bonus buffs. Can be followed by Seraphic Execution Stage 2.
- Cooldown: 13s
- Concerto Energy regeneration: 10

## Galbrena: Resonance Skill Multipliers (Lv. 1)
- Encroach DMG: 5.40% + 12.60%
- Ascent of Malice DMG: 25.94% + 25.94%
- Concerto Regen on Ascent of Malice: 10

## Galbrena: Resonance Liberation: Hellfire Absolution
Attack the target dealing Fusion DMG (Echo Skill DMG).
On cast while in Demon Hypostasis, grants +85% DMG Multiplier increase to: Basic Attack – Seraphic Execution, Heavy Attack – Flamewing Verdict, Mid-air Attack – Hellsent Barrage, and Dodge Counter – Purgatory Scourge for 14 seconds.
- Resonance Energy Cost: 125
- Cooldown: 25s
- Concerto Regen: 20
- Can be cast mid-air close to ground
- Note: Must be cast BEFORE entering Demon Hypostasis to take advantage of the DMG multiplier buff; also best cast after the 20% ATK buff from Burning Drive is fully stacked

## Galbrena: Resonance Liberation Multipliers (Lv. 1)
- Hellfire Absolution DMG: 55.79% + 45.64% × 11

## Galbrena: Forte Circuit: Beyond Threshold — Enhanced State Attacks
All attacks in Demon Hypostasis replace standard Threshold State counterparts and consume Purging Flame on hit.

**Basic Attack – Seraphic Execution:** Up to 5 consecutive attacks; Stages 1–3 Heavy Attack DMG; Stages 4–5 Echo Skill DMG; Stage 5 → Stage 3 loop
**Heavy Attack – Flamewing Verdict:** Up to 3 shots; Stage 3 Echo Skill DMG; STA cost 10 per stage
**Mid-air Attack – Hellsent Barrage:** Aerial plunge or sustained fire; Heavy Attack DMG; STA cost 30 (sustained 20/sec)
**Dodge Counter – Purgatory Scourge:** Heavy Attack DMG; leads into Seraphic Execution Stage 4
**Resonance Skill – Ravage:** Same as Encroach but in Demon Hypostasis; shares cooldown with Encroach (5s)
**Hellstride:** Press Dodge during own skill to deal fixed Fusion DMG (Basic Attack DMG, unaffected by DMG buffs); enables successful dodge; STA cost 20; cannot be cast consecutively

