## Galbrena: Resonance Chain: Sequence Node 1 (S1)
When casting Resonance Skill – Ascent of Malice, each point of Afterflame additionally grants +2% CRIT DMG to Seraphic Execution, Flamewing Verdict, Hellsent Barrage, Ravage, and Purgatory Scourge, up to +80%. Removed on exiting Demon Hypostasis.
Additionally, Seraphic Execution Stage 5, Flamewing Verdict Stage 3, and Hellsent Barrage become immune to interruption in Demon Hypostasis.

## Galbrena: Resonance Chain: Sequence Node 2 (S2)
Burning Drive passive grants 350% more ATK Bonus (i.e., effectively +90% ATK instead of +20%).

## Galbrena: Resonance Chain: Sequence Node 3 (S3)
Resonance Liberation DMG Multiplier is increased by 130%.

## Galbrena: Resonance Chain: Sequence Node 4 (S4)
When Resonators on the team cast Echo Skill, all Resonators gain +20% all-Attribute DMG Bonus for 20s.

## Galbrena: Resonance Chain: Sequence Node 5 (S5)
DMG Multipliers of Encroach, Ascent of Malice, and Ravage increased by 150%.

## Galbrena: Resonance Chain: Sequence Node 6 (S6)
Demon Hypostasis becomes Eternal Hypostasis (retains all prior effects).
- In Eternal Hypostasis, DMG Multipliers of Seraphic Execution, Flamewing Verdict, Hellsent Barrage, and Purgatory Scourge are additionally increased by +60%.
- For every 1 point of Afterflame consumed on casting Ascent of Malice, Seraphic Execution, Flamewing Verdict, Hellsent Barrage, Ravage, and Purgatory Scourge gain +0.875% Fusion DMG Amplification (up to +35%), removed on exiting Eternal Hypostasis.

## Galbrena: Best Echo Set: Flamewing's Shadow
3-set: Dealing Echo Skill DMG increases Heavy Attack CRIT Rate by +20% for 6s. Dealing Heavy Attack DMG increases Echo Skill CRIT Rate by +20% for 6s. While both effects are active, gain +16% Fusion DMG Bonus.
- This set is uniquely tailored to Galbrena's dual Echo Skill / Heavy Attack scaling and is rated as her best-in-slot set.
- Recommended pairing: 3p Flamewing's Shadow + 2p Molten Rift or Flaming Clawprint
- Main Echo: Corrosaurus (4-cost) — provides 20% Echo DMG, 12% Fusion DMG Bonus, and an active Echo Skill cast for Afterflame generation
- Echo Stat Priority: 4-cost → CRIT DMG / CRIT Rate; 3-cost → Fusion DMG / ATK%; 1-cost → ATK%
- Substat Priority: Energy Regen (to threshold) > CRIT Rate = CRIT DMG > ATK% > ATK > Heavy Attack DMG%

## Galbrena: Signature Weapon: Lux & Umbra
- Type: Pistols (5-star)
- Stats at Lv. 90: ATK 587, CRIT DMG 48.6%
- Passive: Provides Fusion DMG Amplification to Heavy Attacks and Echo Skills in tandem; stacking both effects triggers additional DEF Ignore bonus
- Tier: 100% (best-in-slot); ~8% performance lead over next-best option

