## Galbrena: Rotation Guide
Standard rotation (12.2 second rotation time, S0):
1. Intro → Basic P2 → Basic P3 → Basic P4 → Basic P2 → Basic P3
2. Resonance Skill: Ascent of Malice (interrupt animation on hit via Ultimate)
3. Ultimate (Hellfire Absolution)
4. Forte: Basic P2 → P3 → P4 → P5 → P3 → P4 → P5 (Swap Cancel on final P5)
5. Outro

- Dodge Counters replace Basic P3 whenever executable, dealing higher damage and consuming more Purging Flame efficiently
- Basic P5 and Ascent of Malice animation can both be early-cancelled to save time without losing damage
- In Demon Hypostasis, skip P1 by starting from P2 (Intro, Ultimate, and P5 all lead into P2)
- Cast Galbrena's active Echo Skill before Ascent of Malice to maximize Afterflame going into Demon Hypostasis

