## Galbrena: Best Teams
- **Best Overall (S0 Budget):** Galbrena + Qiuyuan + Shorekeeper (/Verina)
  - Qiuyuan provides Echo Skill DMG buffs and additional Afterflame charge via his Echo Skills
- **Mono Fusion:** Galbrena + Brant (or Mortefi) + Lupa
  - Lupa enables Fusion archetype bonus and Sinflame pre-loading before Galbrena's Intro
  - Mortefi is the more accessible option; Brant scales better at high investment
- **Alt Premium:** Galbrena + Phrolova + Iuno + Shorekeeper/Verina
  - Phrolova contributes additional Echo Skill casts (Afterflame) and 25% Heavy DMG Amplify on Outro
- **F2P:** Galbrena + Mortefi + Shorekeeper (/Verina)

## Galbrena: Galbrena's Weaknesses
- Struggles in Whimpering Wastes multi-wave content due to damage being heavily loaded into the last two-thirds of her rotation (burst-style rather than sustained AoE)
- Very limited weapon selection: only her signature Lux & Umbra and the standard banner's Static Mist are naturally ideal for her split Echo Skill / Heavy Attack scaling
- Kit's simple playstyle (Basic Attack spam + Dodge Counter) can feel monotonous to some players

